{"tid":1180120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江蘇幼兒園「掃黑除惡」　35 名幼兒被查　當局被轟形式主義","createTime":"2019-05-31T14:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T07:59:00.000Z","uid":208722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25bce643548bdafbf80d6147af615aaa2e572502","tid":1180120,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E5%9C%92%E3%80%8C%E6%8E%83%E9%BB%91%E9%99%A4%E6%83%A1%E3%80%8D%E3%80%8035+%E5%90%8D%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%9F%A5%E3%80%80%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E8%BD%9F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9-po8Nll?utm_source=fbshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%259C%2592%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258E%2583%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%2583%25A1%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%258035%2B%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%2585%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%259F%25A5%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25BE%25A9-po8Nll%3Futm_source%3Dfbshare&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=e21c0aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E5%9C%92%E3%80%8C%E6%8E%83%E9%BB%91%E9%99%A4%E6%83%A1%E3%80%8D%E3%80%8035+%E5%90%8D%E5%B9%BC%E5%85%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%9F%A5%E3%80%80%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E8%BD%9F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9-po8Nll?utm_source=fbshare</a><br />\n<br />\n中國近年大力推動「掃黑除惡專項鬥爭」，要求全國上下打擊黑社會。不過近日就連江蘇無錫一間幼兒園都成為「掃黑除惡」的目標，校內35名幼兒被查。事件在網上引來熱議，當局則解釋是信息傳遞出錯，並就事件向家長道歉。<br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳一張相片，可見一份文件上寫有「無錫市新光幼兒園掃黑除惡專項鬥爭」，要求幼兒園的班主任填寫該表格，匯報「學生是否涉黑涉惡情況摸排」情況。回覆則寫道「通過對本班35名幼兒進行排查，未發現有幼兒有涉黑涉惡情況」。表格上亦附有幼兒園班主任老師的簽名。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起微博網民熱議，不少人都批評當局形式主義導致今次鬧劇：「這絕對是形式主義到了極端」、「地方官員為了迎合和回應上級下達的『打黑除惡』口號，不管做什麼是都能往『打黑除惡』上靠」、「社會主義的形式主義，上面要求的，一定要做的」。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇省無錫市委宣傳部證實網上流傳的文件屬實，但解釋稱是資訊傳遞中出現錯誤，行動原本是為了杜絕校園欺淩現象。轄區教育部門已要求該校進行整改，並向家長說明及道歉，同時吸取教訓。"},{"pid":"71994bd7b77b82c0e021c6b5a5c31a452a4ffab3","tid":1180120,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iIix32v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiIix32v.jpg&h=93910757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b35ac657e73b18130703e2f1da603ee6dacfa7d","tid":1180120,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"反革命幼童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708b3c63425647306d43a79c6a405cdfb7f83868","tid":1180120,"uid":40478,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"文革果時玩過<br />\n每個單位都要交反革命名單<br />\n包括幼稚園同老人院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d95a394a55c457de6841b32823968acc1448b38","tid":1180120,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec929469f5dc5f42ec229f494b8ea1b8043f24d7","tid":1180120,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"細細個已經開始訓練起朵斬人"},{"pid":"f77d7008a334a2ce7499ff22a536da86cc5811f2","tid":1180120,"uid":103156,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNQR053.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNQR053.png&h=4cfba590&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f99bc85983fae6cd8e7adac3c8ed86bca193efd","tid":1180120,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec929469f5dc5f42ec229f494b8ea1b8043f24d7","tid":1180120,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"細細個已經開始訓練起朵斬人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"大清幼童留美記"},{"pid":"9246e2a2a039850ccc5d36eb909d7c6cffd84898","tid":1180120,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"消滅於萌芽狀態"}]}